words and figures “Part XIV of Chapter VI of the Finance Act, 2017 (7 of 2017), shall be governed by the provisions of the section 184 of that Act”, the words and figures “the Tribunal Reforms Act, 2021, shall
be governed by the provisions of Chapter II of the said Act” shall be substituted.`)
  (str footnotes) (str )
  (str query) (str abv=CEN&statehandle=123456789/1362&actid=AC_CEN_2_2_00040_202133_1629961891898&sectionId=57380&sectionno=26&orderno=26&orgactid=AC_CEN_2_2_00040_202133_1629961891898)
